(847, 1, '2016-08-19 11:52:32', '2016-08-19 11:52:32', '[tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" module_class=\"custom-h3\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Blurb</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" custom_margin=\"65px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"45px||40px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"40px||0px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"The Start and the Art Direction\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ff3f1c\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#0d0d0d\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#ff3f1c\" image=\"your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon7-1.png\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_font_size=\"30\" custom_margin_phone=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" body_font_size=\"17\" header_font=\"|on|||\" custom_margin=\"||74px|\" custom_margin_laptop=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWhile I still was a student I had been working on few simple projects, creating landing pages for small and medium local businesses in my home city of Brisbane, Australia. As I progressed I started my work at one of the biggest full cycle web studios in Australia and NZ. My well thought through, visually appealing designs, enhanced by subtle details and brand...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"62px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"]\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"UI and UX Design That Stands Out\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ff3f1c\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#0d0d0d\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#ff3f1c\" image=\"your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon8-1.png\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_font_size=\"30\" custom_margin_phone=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" body_font_size=\"17\" header_font=\"|on|||\" custom_margin=\"||74px|\" custom_margin_laptop=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA customer-centered thinking and the love for design turned out to be an effective combo when collaborating with agencies, clients and brands. I always enjoy developing digital concepts and solving problems that pop up during the production stage... This rough framework represents my pathway to a balanced understanding of the web design as it is and as it should be!</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"62px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"]\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_gri