rder_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_font_size=\"30\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" body_font_size=\"17\" header_font=\"|on|||\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_padding=\"53px|30px|40px|30px\" custom_padding_laptop=\"40px|20px|20px|20px\" custom_padding_tablet=\"20px|20px|20px|20px\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIn just about 20 years the world of web design has transformed from a minuscule industry that crafted scary pages with content.</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Designing Prints\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ff3f1c\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#0d0d0d\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#ff3f1c\" image=\"your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon31.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_font_size=\"30\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" body_font_size=\"17\" header_font=\"|on|||\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_padding=\"53px|30px|40px|30px\" custom_padding_laptop=\"40px|20px|20px|20px\" custom_padding_tablet=\"20px|20px|20px|20px\" custom_padding_phone=\"20px|20px|20px|20px\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nI specialize in print design solutions which creatively integrate all aspects of visual communication to strengthen your brand and corporate image.</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#cecece\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"60px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"50px|||\" custom_margin_phone=\"32px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_laptop=\"55px|||\"]\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider]