(4186, 1, '2017-02-23 16:18:41', '2017-02-23 16:18:41', '[tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" custom_margin=\"65px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"45px||40px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"40px||0px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" template_type=\"row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"The Start and the Art Direction\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ff3f1c\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#0d0d0d\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#ff3f1c\" image=\"your_website_url_here/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon7-1.png\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_font_size=\"30\" custom_margin_phone=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" body_font_size=\"17\" header_font=\"|on|||\" custom_margin=\"||74px|\" custom_margin_laptop=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\"]\n\n<p>\nWhile I still was a student I had been working on few simple projects, creating landing pages for small and medium local businesses in my home city of Brisbane, Australia. As I progressed I started my work at one of the biggest full cycle web studios in Australia and NZ. My well thought through, visually appealing designs, enhanced by subtle details and brand...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"UI and UX Design That Stands Out\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ff3f1c\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_col